    - pip
    - jupyter-packaging

    - ipywidgets >=7.0.0

  commands:

    - test -f ${PREFIX}/share/jupyter/labextensions/ipannotoryous/package.json                            # [unix]

    - if not exist %PREFIX%\\share\\jupyter\\labextensions\\ipannotoryous\\package.json (exit 1)          # [win]
